fields.name: Total calories + macros
fields.formula:
concat(
    sum(lookup('Meals eaten', 'Calories')), 
    ' 🔥 / ',
    sum(lookup('Meals eaten', 'Protein (g)')), 
    'g 🥩 / ',
    sum(lookup('Meals eaten', 'Carbs (g)')), 
    'g 🥔 / ',
    sum(lookup('Meals eaten', 'Fats (g)')), 
    'g 🧈'
)

fields.name: Number of sad days
fields.formula: count(filter(lookup('All days', 'Overall mood'), totext(lookup('All days', 'Overall mood')) = 'Sad'))

fields.name: Number of happy days
fields.formula: count(filter(lookup('All days', 'Overall mood'), totext(lookup('All days', 'Overall mood')) = 'Happy'))
